oai_dc:dc.dc:title: East Nashville High School baseball squad of Nashville, Tennessee, 1937
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: A Spring of 1937 photograph of the East Nashville High School baseball squad, Nashville, Tennessee. The verso lists the names of the players and coach: (sitting) Weaver, Tanksley, Cothern, Gonzales, Bohan, Voorhies, Martin; (standing) Demrick, Greek, Logan, Bullard, Brooks, Hooper, Seats, Wand, Stidham, and Coach Armstead. Forms part of the Nashville Room Historic Photographs Collection. 1 photograph : b & w ; 8 x 10 in.
